  "body": "# Issue\r\nThe current spec does not gracefully handle the case in which a committee has not successfully included any attestations on chain at the current or next epoch boundaries.\r\n\r\nSpecifically, the usage of `winning_hash` is under specified when the set of possible `shard_block_root`s from the committee is empty.\r\n\r\nThere might be some other cases to consider. Leaving digging into possible other cases as part of this issue.",
